title: Cook.Redirect
body:
<<Textbox>>
<<Name|Cook>>
<<Portrait|cook_happy>>
How you doin',Cap?
<</Textbox>>

[[That's all.|Cook.ByeD]]

[[Can you tell me about $CLUE?|Cook.QuestioningD]]

title: Cook.QuestioningD
body:
<<Textbox>>
<<Name|Captain>>
Jorji, I found this $CLUE. Can you tell me anything about it?
<</Textbox>>

<<Textbox>>
<<Name|Cook>>
<<Portrait|cook_neutral>>
You know who's good with that stuff?
<</Textbox>>


[[Forget it.|Cook.ByeD]]

[[Who is?|Cook.AnswerD]]

title: Cook.AnswerD
body:
<<Textbox>>
<<Name|Captain>>
No, who is?
<</Textbox>>

<<Textbox>>
<<Name|Cook>>
<<Portrait|cook_neutral>>
$CREWMATE. $CREWMATE would know.
<</Textbox>>

<<Textbox>>
<<Name|Captain>>
Thanks Jorji.
<</Textbox>>

<<Textbox>>
<<Name|Cook>>
<<Portrait|cook_neutral>>
Anytime, Cap.
<</Textbox>>

//End
